begin
reserve T for TopSpace;
theorem
Th1: (for A,B being (Subset of T) holds (( A \/ B ) = ( [#] T ) iff ( A ` ) c= B))
proof
let A being (Subset of T);
let B being (Subset of T);
A1:now
assume ( A ` ) c= B;
then ( A \/ ( A ` ) ) c= ( A \/ B ) by XBOOLE_1:9;
then ( [#] T ) c= ( A \/ B ) by PRE_TOPC:2;
hence ( A \/ B ) = ( [#] T ) by XBOOLE_0:def 10;
end;
now
assume ( A \/ B ) = ( [#] T );
then ( ( [#] T ) \ A ) = ( B \ A ) by XBOOLE_1:40;
hence ( A ` ) c= B by XBOOLE_1:36;
end;
hence thesis by A1;
end;
